{"tid":1741964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭文傑爆料之後 大家有處理中共間諜嘅準備未？","createTime":"2019-11-20T14:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T06:21:01.000Z","uid":4493,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1894ac2377b114a23779cc5ddad50d651006b214","tid":1741964,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"基本上證明左：<br />\n<br />\n1. 有香港手足被送咗上大陸 （被捕或綁架）<br />\n2. 中共用咗非常殘酷嘅手法對待佢哋<br />\n3. 佢哋能力製造罪名證據 冇辦法由合法途徑追討<br />\n<br />\n其實支共嘅情報人員水平唔係好高<br />\n六月七月嗰時好多都比人發現 不過手足多數放走 最多都係打爆電話<br />\n<br />\n呢啲國安國保就係殺人唔眨眼 用滿清十大酷刑虐殺手足嘅 可能好多已經殺過人 我哋香港嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n下次再見到 大家準備好報仇未？<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最低消費打斷手腳 手足埋佢單都唔會阻止<br />\n<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係要保持理性 佢又冇做過乜嘢 打爛電話就放走啦"},{"pid":"f92caf07a7c4f7c67a7263e1e896c1b4a7874dcd","tid":1741964,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbaf4ac1f47a3a3ed9b20c6f212b3498e2d7831","tid":1741964,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"最低消費要用返被自殺呢招"},{"pid":"4b2af62105b7ba1686a88126b2962258ce2b197e","tid":1741964,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GnOMRad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnOMRad.jpg&h=78ac2ebd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43282c9d40041b27a779a388a115ce5d66c3b4c7","tid":1741964,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fbaf4ac1f47a3a3ed9b20c6f212b3498e2d7831","tid":1741964,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:40:25.000Z","msg":"最低消費要用返被自殺呢招"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:42:07.000Z","msg":"我就話直接埋佢單冇仇報<br />\n支那一定唔敢煲大佢"},{"pid":"1d50b92fafecd4cfd4056e76279f